dct_title_s: A map of China prepared for the China Inland Mission
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Shows locations of Protestant missions. Inset: England on the same scale. Originally folded in cover 22 x 13 cm. On cover: "Come over and help us." Historic Maps copy has stamp of Maclay & Co., Tientsin, China.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published by the China Inland Mission, 4 Pyrland Road, N., 1894.
